parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Premature Engine Seal and Gasket Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature failure of engine seals and gaskets can lead to oil leaks, engine damage, and potentially cause engine compartment fires, which can result in vehicle damage, injury, or even death.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: TRAP Oxidizer Failure and Related Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the TRAP oxidizer can cause damage to the head gaskets, leading to engine damage and potentially causing engine compartment fires.

the transmission shifter can be moved into different gears with the ignition off
